HEADWORD: Alburnum
<hw>Al*bur"num</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>albus</ets> white.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The white and
softer part of wood, between the inner bark and the hard wood or
duramen; sapwood.</def>⟦br⟧
